Camera End Date: Folder End Date (Date of last image in folder, can fill out at end (YYYY-MM-DD)
CameraName: Can fill this out exactly how it looks on the folder, no spaces then drag down the column at end
Location Code: 3 Letter code for locations-DO NOT ENTER, THIS WILL FILL AUTOMATICALLY
Image#: Please start with IMG in the image name
Image Quality: 1 High, 2 Okay, 3 Bad/can barely see animal
Species: coyote, human, raccoon, skunk, opossum, woodrat, bobcat, bird (note species if possible), squirrel, ground squirrel, vehicle, or unknown
SpeciesCode: Four letter code for species-DO NOT ENTER, THIS WILL FILL AUTOMATICALLY
# of Individuals: number of animals seen in image
Time: 24 hours, convert if needed, so 1PM would be 13 etc.    Military Hours-->hh:mm:ss
Notes: Please record anything noteworthy-prey, young ones, weather problems, if it's a cool picture for outreach or instagram please put "COOL" in the notes column
